\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {(Wis; Trained Only; Psion, Psychic Warrior Only)
\par Check: The DC and effect depend on the task attempted.
\par 
\par Task\tab \tab \tab DC
\par Resist fear\tab \tab 15
\par Memorize\tab \tab 13
